00:28:22,110 --> 00:28:24,070
It took our Sangyi students

566
00:28:24,090 --> 00:28:25,940
three years

567
00:28:25,970 --> 00:28:28,120
to achieve this level of success.

568
00:28:30,970 --> 00:28:32,660
You won't blame me, will you?

569
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,520
How could I blame you?

570
00:28:34,550 --> 00:28:36,280
You've already done your best.

571
00:28:36,570 --> 00:28:38,370
It's them who used underhanded tactics.

572
00:28:38,370 --> 00:28:40,130
For the third round,

573
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:41,650
"Melodic Recognition."

574
00:28:41,710 --> 00:28:44,370
Both sides, please send out your participants.

575
00:28:45,230 --> 00:28:45,910
This is bad.

576
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:49,510
