580
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:00,600
Well.

581
00:29:00,650 --> 00:29:02,280
Since it's certain we'll lose,

582
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:03,990
the punishment is unavoidable.

583
00:29:03,990 --> 00:29:05,160
So, I might as well go up

584
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:06,620
and end this competition.

585
00:29:13,850 --> 00:29:15,410
Go. Do your best!

586
00:29:15,840 --> 00:29:16,860
He's trying to

587
00:29:16,900 --> 00:29:19,430
